content: I am genuinely asking you if you stand with people like this, please hop off my Twitter feed. Political discourse is one thing. This is beyond reprehensible and disgusting.,https://,twitter.com/Acosta/status/,1024467940257738752, ,…

As a member of of the Florida news media, I try to look everyone in the eye at these rallies.  I do my best to tell the real story that is going on at these even though I will be screamed at and pushed by Trump supporters as I walk out to file my story.
Please, stop reporting on these rallies. Nobody cares.
The thing is, people do.  What you are asking is to stop what literally my job entails. If I’m not there to report on the truth then it goes silent in the dark.
